title: REFILE-Shenzhen Infinova to raise up to 752 mln yuan in private placement
text:
(Refiles to add link)
Sept 10 (Reuters) - Shenzhen Infinova Ltd
* Says plans to raise up to 752 million yuan ($117.92 million) in private placement of shares to fund projects, shares to resume trading on Sept 11
Source text in Chinese: bit.ly/1MduGrQ ; bit.ly/1gbfSLQ
 ($1 = 6.3770 Chinese yuan renminbi) (Reporting by Hong Kong and Singapore newsrooms)
